OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin Australia tour
OL,4,Cwith visit to children's hospital
OL,6,FThe Duke and Duchess of Sussex hugged
OL,7,Fpatients at a children's hospital as
OL,8,Fthe couple kicked-off their tour of
OL,9,FAustralia on Tuesday.
OL,11,FHarry and Meghan were cheered by large
OL,12,Fcrowds gathered along the walkways of
OL,13,Fthe Royal Children's Hospital in
OL,14,FMelbourne as they spoke to children
OL,15,Fand posed for photographs with
OL,16,Fpatients.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
