FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776255072
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin Australia tour
OL,4,Cwith visit to children's hospital
OL,6,FThe Sussexes' office said their four-
OL,7,Fday visit, which has been privately
OL,8,Ffunded, will "focus on mental health,
OL,9,Fcommunity resilience, and support for
OL,10,Fveterans and their families, alongside
OL,11,Fprivate meetings and special projects".
OL,13,FHarry and Meghan's trip has whipped up
OL,14,Fintense interest among the Australian
OL,15,Fmedia, with a mass of reporters
OL,16,Fstanding by as the couple entered the
OL,17,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
