OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin Australia tour
OL,4,Cwith visit to children's hospital
OL,6,FWhile greeting crowds at the hospital,
OL,7,FHarry hugged Christina Parkes, who
OL,8,Fworks as an academic at the University
OL,9,Fof Melbourne and whose 13-year-old
OL,10,Fdaughter Adelaide is a patient at the
OL,11,Fhospital.
OL,13,FSpeaking before the couple arrived, Ms
OL,14,FParkes said it "means an enormous
OL,15,Famount" to have the couple visit
OL,16,FAustralia, adding: "I'm absolutely
OL,17,Fthrilled to see the couple.
OL,26,@xD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776255072
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin Australia tour
OL,4,Cwith visit to children's hospital
OL,6,F"Harry's grandmother actually opened
OL,7,Fthe hospital originally, and her
OL,8,Fportrait and his grandfather's
OL,9,Fportrait are in the hallway.
OL,11,F"I cannot overstate how important the
OL,12,Fwork is that they do here at the
OL,13,Fchildren's hospital because my
OL,14,Fdaughter wouldn't be here without
OL,15,Fthem."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
