OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin Australia tour
OL,4,Cwith visit to children's hospital
OL,6,FAmong those greeting Harry and Meghan
OL,7,Fat the hospital was four-year-old
OL,8,Fpatient Lily, who gave a flower to the
OL,9,Fduchess and presented the couple with
OL,10,Fa hand-drawn sign that said: "Welcome
OL,11,FHarry and Meghan."
OL,13,F"Oh my gosh, this is so sweet. I love
OL,14,Fit," said Meghan as she hugged the
OL,15,Fgirl.
OL,17,FThe pair toured the hospital wards,
OL,18,Fwith the duke discussing Aussie rules
OL,19,Ffootball with 17-year-old oncology
OL,20,Fpatient Hamish.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
