OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin Australia tour
OL,4,Cwith visit to children's hospital
OL,6,FMaya, 17, another patient at the
OL,7,Fhospital said she was "very excited"
OL,8,Fto meet the duke and duchess, adding:
OL,9,F"My grandma's a big fan so we're doing
OL,10,Fthis for her just so we can say we saw
OL,11,Fthem ` she'll be thrilled.
OL,13,F"It means a lot. Just to know that
OL,14,Fthey're worried about us, they love
OL,15,Fus, just to know that they love
OL,16,FAustralia and Melbourne, it's really
OL,17,Fnice."
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
