OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin Australia tour
OL,4,Cwith visit to children's hospital
OL,6,FHarry's parents, the King and Diana,
OL,7,FPrincess of Wales, visited the Royal
OL,8,FChildren's Hospital in 1985, meeting
OL,9,Fpatients while on a visit to the state
OL,10,Fof Victoria.
OL,12,FThe hospital's new site was opened in
OL,13,FOctober 2011 by Queen Elizabeth II,
OL,14,Fwho met with patients during her visit
OL,15,Fon her royal tour of Australia with
OL,16,FPrince Philip.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776255072
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin Australia tour
OL,4,Cwith visit to children's hospital
OL,6,FThe late Queen opened the earlier
OL,7,Fiteration of the hospital in February
OL,8,F1963 ` with the hospital pushing
OL,9,Fforward its opening by six months to
OL,10,Fensure it would align with the royal
OL,11,Ftour.
OL,13,FHarry and Meghan took part in a garden
OL,14,Ftherapy session with patients at the
OL,15,Fhospital, smelling plants and flowers.
OL,17,FAsked if he would like to take some
OL,18,Fgumtree home, Harry joked: "I would,
OL,19,Fbut I think I'd probably get arrested
OL,20,Fat some point."
OL,26,@zD@\OU|D@OO]
