OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin Australia tour
OL,4,Cwith visit to children's hospital
OL,6,FFollowing the hospital visit, the
OL,7,Fduchess visited a women's refuge in
OL,8,Fthe city.
OL,10,FDressed in an apron, Meghan served
OL,11,Ffrittata to people at the centre, run
OL,12,Fby McAuley Community Services for
OL,13,FWomen, which supports women and
OL,14,Fchildren experiencing family violence,
OL,15,Fhomelessness and related challenges.
OL,17,FJoining people at a table eating food
OL,18,Fat the centre, Meghan told them: "We
OL,19,Flanded here this morning so my jet lag
OL,20,Fhasn't quite hit yet."
OL,26,@zD@bOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
