OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin Australia tour
OL,4,Cwith visit to children's hospital
OL,6,FLater on Tuesday Harry and Meghan
OL,7,Fvisited Melbourne's National Veterans
OL,8,FArts Museum to view an exhibition of
OL,9,Fartwork created by veterans.
OL,11,FThere, the Sussexes also took part in
OL,12,Fa model making activity with veterans
OL,13,Fand their families.
OL,15,FIt is understood that Harry and
OL,16,FMeghan's privately funded visit will
OL,17,Fnot include general walkabouts to meet
OL,18,Fthe public.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
