OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin Australia tour
OL,4,Cwith visit to children's hospital
OL,6,FThe couple are also expected to join
OL,7,Fmembers of the Invictus community on
OL,8,Fthe water in Sydney Harbour, and in
OL,9,FCanberra, Harry will attend
OL,10,Fengagements at the Australian War
OL,11,FMemorial.
OL,13,FHarry and Meghan also have engagements
OL,14,Fwith Movember and Australian mental
OL,15,Fhealth organisation Batyr.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
