OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin Australia tour
OL,4,Cwith visit to children's hospital
OL,6,FBoth the Duke and Duchess will be
OL,7,Fspeaking at separate ticketed events.
OL,9,FMeghan will be interviewed on stage at
OL,10,Fa "girls' weekend" retreat in Sydney,
OL,11,Fcosting #1,400 a ticket.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Harry will be a guest
OL,14,Fspeaker on Thursday at the InterEdge
OL,15,FSummit, which explores the
OL,16,F"intersection of leadership,
OL,17,Fpsychosocial safety and human
OL,18,Fconnection in the workplace".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
