OL,3,CHarry and Meghan begin Australia tour
OL,4,Cwith visit to children's hospital
OL,6,FDelegate tickets for the summit,
OL,7,Fhosted at Melbourne's Centrepiece
OL,8,Fconference venue, are available for
OL,9,F#525, with platinum tickets costing
OL,10,F#1,250 and a virtual ticket allowing
OL,11,Fon-demand access to Harry's speech
OL,12,Fcosting #260.
OL,14,FFinally, the visit will conclude at a
OL,15,Frugby fixture in Sydney between New
OL,16,FSouth Wales Waratahs and Moana
OL,17,FPasifika at the Allianz Stadium on
OL,18,FFriday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
